<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>E-Learning Management System</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#0d1117;
color:white;
}

header{
background:#161b22;
padding:15px 50px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
position:sticky;
top:0;
}

header h2{
color:#58a6ff;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:20px;
}

nav a:hover{
color:#58a6ff;
}

.hero{
height:90vh;
background:url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80") center/cover;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
}

.overlay{
background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);
padding:40px;
border-radius:15px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:50px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:20px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

button{
padding:12px 25px;
background:#238636;
border:none;
color:white;
font-size:17px;
border-radius:8px;
cursor:pointer;
}

button:hover{
background:#2ea043;
}

section{
padding:60px;
}

.title{
text-align:center;
font-size:35px;
margin-bottom:40px;
color:#58a6ff;
}

.cards{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:25px;
}

.card{
background:#161b22;
padding:20px;
border-radius:12px;
text-align:center;
transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.card img{
width:100%;
height:170px;
border-radius:10px;
}

.card h3{
margin:15px 0;
}

.about{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:30px;
align-items:center;
}

.about img{
width:400px;
border-radius:10px;
}

.about div{
flex:1;
}

.contact input,
.contact textarea{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin:10px 0;
background:#21262d;
border:none;
color:white;
border-radius:8px;
}

footer{
background:#161b22;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
margin-top:30px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

header{
flex-direction:column;
}

.about{
flex-direction:column;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:35px;
}

}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>

<h2>E-Learning</h2>

<nav>

<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Courses</a>
<a href="#">About</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>

</nav>

</header>

<div class="hero">

<div class="overlay">

<h1>Learn Anytime, Anywhere</h1>

<p>Build your future with online education.</p>

<button>Start Learning</button>

</div>

</div>

<section>

<h2 class="title">Popular Courses</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?w=600">

<h3>HTML & CSS</h3>

<p>Learn web designing from scratch.</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?w=600">

<h3>JavaScript</h3>

<p>Create dynamic websites easily.</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515879218367-8466d910aaa4?w=600">

<h3>Python</h3>

<p>Master Python programming.</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2 class="title">About Us</h2>

<div class="about">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?w=700">

<div>

<h2>Why Choose Our LMS?</h2>

<p>
We provide high-quality online courses with expert instructors,
video lessons, quizzes, certificates, and project-based learning.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2 class="title">Contact Us</h2>

<div class="contact">

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">

<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email">

<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>

<button>Send Message</button>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<h3>© 2026 E-Learning Management System</h3>

<p>Designed with HTML & CSS</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
